0, "department": "Customer Success", "relevance_score": 1.0, "created_at": "2026-07-07T15:13:45.574503+00:00", "last_accessed_at": "2026-07-07T15:13:45.574532+00:00", "label": "Knowledge", "id": "1b0a98ea-f9dd-4b9e-a997-5d64dc579fd8"}, {"org_id": "33113e15-5821-48d5-b339-3ca220af3f48", "title": "FreshCorp Finance & Compensation Policy 2026", "domain": "finance", "source_type": "document", "summary": "This document outlines FreshCorp's pay structure, expense reimbursement rules, budget allocations, equity grants, and financial risk considerations for 2026. It tells employees how salaries are set, how travel and meal costs are reimbursed, how much of the budget goes to each department, and the basics of stock vesting and customer concentration risk. The policies are meant to ensure transparent compensation and prudent financial management.", "tags": ["salary bands", "expense reimbursement", "budget allocation", "equity vesting", "financial risk"], "access_count": 0, "department": null, "relevance_score": 1.0, "created_at": "2026-07-15T01:17:57.688496+00:00", "last_accessed_at": "2026-07-15T01:17:57.688507+00:00", "label": "Knowledge", "id": "43493f1e-a7de-4eb9-afb8-514b26452b1c"}, {"org_id": "a6611ac4-8f15-44f3-baac-abdf8dd182a4", "title": "FreshCorp Finance & Compensation Policy 2026", "domain": "finance", "source_type": "document", "summary": "This document outlines FreshCorp's 2026 compensation structure, expense reimbursement rules, budget allocations, equity grants, and financial risk considerations. It tells employees how salaries and commissions are set, how to get reimbursed for work\u2011related costs, how the company\u2019s budget is divided, and what equity and risk factors apply. Understanding it helps staff know their pay, benefits, and the financial health of the company.", "tags": ["salary", "expense", "budget", "equity", "risk"], "access_count": 0, "department": null, "relevance_score": 1.0, "created_at": "2026-07-15T01:26:55.200632+00:00", "last_acces